Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_reduce_...arcs_threshold(25.10)  timing_reduce_...arcs_threshold(25.10)

Name
       timing_reduce_multi_drive_net_arcs_threshold

Syntax
       timing_reduce_multi_drive_net_arcs_threshold <int>

       Default: 10000

       Sets a threshold number that is used to trigger the reduction of timing
       arcs  of  nets driven by parallel buffers. The reduction takes place if
       the number of arcs is greater than the threshold  value  and  when  the
       timing_reduce_multi_drive_net_arcs global variable is set to true.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

